title: Darkest Africa
actors: Clyde Beatty, Manuel King, Elaine Shepard, Lucien Prival, Wheeler Oakman, Edward McWade, Edmund Cobb, Ray Turner, Donald Reed
description: A 15-episode serial in which Beatty goes to darkest Africa to rescue the Goddess of Joba, who is being held by the high priest.
